== 赤潮 ==
{{main|赤潮}}
[[赤潮|赤潮]]是因為海水被諸如膝溝藻屬物種這類有顏色的細胞在海洋中泛濫，從而令海水看起來像變了顏色似的。部分膝溝藻屬物種會產生毒素。舉例說：[[具刺膝沟藻|具刺膝沟藻]]（''Gonyaulax spinifera''）已知與{{tsl|en|yessotoxin|扇貝毒素}}（{{lang|en|yessotoxin}}；YTX）的生成相關；而扇貝毒素是一組在結構上與[[聚醚|聚醚]]（[[polyether|polyether]]）相關的毒素，能夠在食用貝殼類生物的體內累積，並產生跟中了[[麻痺性貝毒|麻痺性貝毒]]（PSP）類似的病徵<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Kirkpatrick |first=Barbara |last2=Fleming |first2=Lora E. |last3=Squicciarini |first3=Dominick |last4=Backer |first4=Lorrie C. |last5=Clark |first5=Richard |last6=Abraham |first6=William |last7=Benson |first7=Janet |last8=Cheng |first8=Yung Sung |last9=Johnson |first9=David |date=2004-04-01 |title=Literature review of Florida red tide: implications for human health effects |journal=Harmful Algae |volume=3 |issue=2 |pages=99–115 |doi=10.1016/j.hal.2003.08.005 |pmc=2856946 |pmid=20411030}}</ref>。

